{"tid":1925314,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉載］濕疹同我入黎 黃店 告急","createTime":"2020-03-14T09:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T17:23:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66781f76b2c26447a45897dd9979ce7acd2f1f47","tid":1925314,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"一間拎30萬出黎幫手既黃店 點解無人知 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就黎捱唔住了</span><br />\n濕疹手足快去懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由細到大皮膚都易敏感 間中有濕疹<br />\n上年成日吸催淚彈 又出汗 痕到仆街 r到損哂<br />\n咁岩見到<span style=\"color: red;\">間黃店派皂比人 話前線 學生 醫護優先 可以幫到敏感</span> 去左攞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wr0zHwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwr0zHwE.jpg&h=70c27d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個店員無sell 都講解左好耐 舖又有文宣 睇得出真心想幫手<br />\n用完又真<span style=\"color: red;\">即晚無咁痕</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日轉季又再番發 <br />\n諗住去懲罰下佢 點知個<span style=\"color: red;\">店員姐姐話就黎捱唔住喇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前派皂用左30萬貨 間旺角分店成日食催淚彈做唔到生意執左 而家又到肺炎一日都無1千生意 業主又唔減租 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">可能4月就執喇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃色經濟圈唔係黃色飲食圈呀<br />\n有濕疹既巴絲睇下 可能幫到你 </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJfgbp3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJfgbp3.jpg&h=b7235b06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb850410fc989a7035f5fbe4758d963f5342414a","tid":1925314,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"整個傳送門俾人地啦：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.deadseamor.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deadseamor.com%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=10a1